description:
Wayne Shorter is presented with the 2009 Distinguished Alumni Achievement Award at NYU Steinhardt's Baccalaureate Ceremony in Honor of the Class of 2009 on Monday, May 11, 2009 at Radio City Music Hall.  

He inspires the graduates with words of wisdom of resistance, mysticism, and Helen Keller.
